s:\\/\\/mayacacoffee.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/04\\/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-2.jpg 602w, https:\\/\\/mayacacoffee.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/04\\/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\\/\\/mayacacoffee.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/04\\/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-2-600x400.jpg 600w\\\" alt=\\\"sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-2\\\" width=\\\"602\\\" height=\\\"402\\\" \\/><\\/p><ol style=\\\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-image: initial; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\\\"><li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Cung c\\u1ea5p c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ed9t l\\u00e0m s\\u1ea1ch nh\\u01b0 : thu\\u1ed1c v\\u1ec7 sinh m\\u00e1y pha d\\u1ea1ng vi\\u00ean, d\\u1ea1ng b\\u1ed9t, d\\u1ea1ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, dung d\\u1ecbch descaling.<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">V\\u1ec7 sinh h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed3ng n\\u1ed3i h\\u01a1i, \\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng, b\\u01a1m \\u00e1p su\\u1ea5t m\\u00e1y pha c\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea.<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">V\\u1ec7 sinh m\\u00e1y pha c\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea, v\\u1ec7 sinh l\\u01b0\\u1edbi l\\u1ecdc m\\u00e1y pha, v\\u00f2i h\\u01a1i b\\u1ecb k\\u1eb9t, t\\u1eafc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, thay th\\u1ebf l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc m\\u00e1y pha c\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea chuy\\u00ean nghi\\u1ec7p.<\\/li><\\/ol><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.8; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\\"><img style=\\\"border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; vertical-align: middle; text-align: center; margin-top: 5px !important; margin-bottom: 5px !important;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/mayacacoffee.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/04\\/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-3.jpg\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 602px) 100vw, 602px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/mayacacoffee.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/04\\/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-3.jpg 602w, https:\\/\\/mayacacoffee.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/04\\/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\\/\\/mayacacoffee.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/04\\/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-3-600x400.jpg 600w\\\" alt=\\\"sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-3\\\" width=\\\"602\\\" height=\\\"402\\\" \\/><br \\/>Nh\\u1eadn s\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa thay th\\u1ebf b\\u01a1m \\u00e1p su\\u1ea5t m\\u00e1y pha c\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea, bo m\\u1ea1nh m\\u00e1y pha c\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea, ron m\\u00e1y pha c\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea c\\u00e1c d\\u00f2ng m\\u00e1y pha La cimbali ,Feama, Breville, Nouva Simonelli, Lelit, Casadio, Mellita, BFC, Royal, Iberital \\u2026 khu v\\u1ef1c mi\\u1ec1n trung v\\u00e0 to\\u00e0n qu\\u1ed1c.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]");
